Outgoing Johannesburg Mayor Herman Mashaba's final day in the office is approaching. JOHANNESBURG - Outgoing Johannesburg Mayor Herman Mashaba's final day in office is approaching. Mashaba is expected to address his last press conference. READ: Maimane, Mashaba belong in the DA: Steenhuisen The Democratic Alliance has announced current MMC for Finance Funzela Ngobeni as its candidate to replace him. Mashaba resigned from the party last month. A new mayor will be elected on 28 November. Outgoing Johannesburg Mayor Herman Mashaba's final day in the office is approaching. Courtesy #DStv403